# Code owners — GitHub auto-requests review from the owner on matching PRs.
# Pairs with branch protection's "require review from Code Owners".
# https://docs.github.com/articles/about-code-owners
#
# Last match wins. @jamesbrock owns everything; the explicit security-sensitive
# paths below exist so that if a second maintainer/team is added later, those
# surfaces still require the primary owner's review.

*                 @jamesbrock

# Security-sensitive surfaces
/.github/         @jamesbrock
/agent/           @jamesbrock
/docker/          @jamesbrock
/scripts/         @jamesbrock
SECURITY.md       @jamesbrock
LICENSE           @jamesbrock
